[h1]Eclectic Traditions[/h1]

This people gather wisdom from every road that crosses their lands. No single way is held above all others, and so all ways are theirs to keep.

[h2]What it does[/h2]
Adds a societal tradition, [b]Eclectic Traditions[/b], and a decision to take it.

[list]
[*] Tradition cap +20.
[*] Cultural acceptance gain +10%.
[*] Cheaper to use as a hybridization parent.
[*] An independent ruler may add it via the [b]Open the Hall to Foreign Customs[/b] decision.
[/list]

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]
[b]CK3 1.19.[/b] Adds new content; does not edit vanilla files.
